subtitleNullable: Top Daily colored original illustrations from Pixiv in 2019
descriptionNullable:
### Dataset Description
The dataset contains popular images (top daily illustrations) from Pixiv in 2019. The main purpose of this dataset is to study color schemes of popular illustrations, thus only filter by using [type](https://github.com/upbit/pixivpy#app-api-60---app-apipixivnet) in pixivpy library. The 'Original' tag ensures no bias of popular characters or series. The top qualifying 68.7k images were collected, unordered on January 15, 2021

The data was collected using the "PixivPy". The Documentation of the library can be found at [here](https://github.com/upbit/pixivpy).

### License
All images in the dataset are copyright to their respective owners.

### Another Dataset

   - Original: [Pixiv Top Daily Illustration 2020](https://www.kaggle.com/stevenevan99/pixiv-top-daily-illustration-2020)

2. Pixiv 2019   
   - Original: [Pixiv Top Daily Illustration 2019](https://www.kaggle.com/stevenevan99/pixiv-top-daily-illustration-2019) (You're Here)
   - Face Only: [Face of Pixiv Top Daily Illustration 2019](https://www.kaggle.com/stevenevan99/face-of-pixiv-top-daily-illustration-2019)
3. Pixiv 2018
   - Original: [Pixiv Top Daily Illustration 2018](https://www.kaggle.com/stevenevan99/pixiv-top-daily-illustration-2018) 
   - Face Only: [Face of Pixiv Top Daily Illustration 2018](https://www.kaggle.com/stevenevan99/face-of-pixiv-top-daily-illustration-2018)
